  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Inside the Atrato: a Film Project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We will make a film and will develop educational materials that draw attention on poverty and environmental degradation in Colombia&apos;s largely forgotten Choco region. The film will show exclusive images of the hard reality of the Atrato together with portraying those who live along the river and are confronted with the environmental and violent social realities of the region. The project will be led by acclaimed artists and environmentalists and its results will be widely disseminated.</narrative>
  </description>
